---
title: Gimbels’ Santa Cheeseburgers with Caramelized Onion, Garlic Mayo & Cheesy Potato Snowballs
description: Unlike the mall Santa at Gimbels, this classic combo of beef and cheese is the real deal. Enjoy juicy cheeseburgers on pillowy potato buns with garlic mayo and topped with balsamic caramelized onion. On the side are cheesy mashed potatoes you’ll roll into “snowballs,” coat in toasted panko breadcrumbs, then stack into potato snow-people. Who says you can’t play with your food? Not us!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/653908a765bc5aac330e060e-37a0a2bb.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/653908a765bc5aac330e060e.pdf
author: Sara Heilman
course: main course
servings: 2
time required: 40 minutes
cuisine: North America
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/gimbels-santa-cheeseburgers-653908a765bc5aac330e060e
nutrition:
  calories: 1300 kcal
